{"title":"希望之歌","authors":["徐燕"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":10,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马鞍山钢铁厂　徐燕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是春雨润绿的新笋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有拔节的希望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是锻锤夯打的铁模，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有成型的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说我折收飞天的翅膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的搏击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能扫退一切的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淡漠、彷徨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自卑、哀唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说已泯灭憧憬的神往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的热燃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会爆出一切的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧迫、坚韧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋发、向上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是新笋，就要拔节生长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是铁模，就要成型闪亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去回答祖国深情的叮咛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去回答人民希冀的目光！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}